title: War of the Roses: The Lost Wedding Ring
description: Tracy's husband claims he lost his wedding ring while walking the dog one day.  Tracy wasn't too suspicious because of that, but then she caught him doing something in the bathroom after he was at his "friend's" house so now she's questioning if he's cheating.
